{{Orphan|date=November 2012}}

'''Stephen Peter Llewellyn''' (18 July 1913&ndash;14 November 1960) was a New Zealand soldier, historian, journalist and novelist. He was born in [[Hereford]], [[Herefordshire]], [[England]] on 18 July 1913.<ref name="DNZB Llewellyn">{{DNZB|title=Stephen Peter Llewellyn|first= Ian|last= McGibbon|id=5l13|accessdate=23 April 2017}}</ref>

